import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import xfeat
from sklearn.manifold import TSNE
import math
%matplotlib inline

lists = pd.read_html('https://m-league.jp/stats')
img_dir = 'image'
df = pd.DataFrame()
teams = ['drivens','EX','sakura','konami','abemas','sega_summy','raiden','u-next']
j = 0
for i in lists:
    data = i
    data = data.T
    data.columns = data.iloc[0]
    data = data[1:]
    data[''] = teams[j]
    j+=1
    df = pd.concat([df,data])
    
data = pd.DataFrame(df['']/df[''],columns = {'/'})
X = df[['','', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '']]
X.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)
# X.drop('index',inplace=True,axis=1)
X.to_csv('corr_dat.csv',index=False)

a = pd.read_csv('corr_dat.csv')
fig,ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(20,8))
sns.heatmap(a.corr(),annot=True)
plt.savefig('corr.png')

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import pickle

#t-SNE
from sklearn.manifold import TSNE

df.reset_index(inplace=True)
index_df = df[['index','']]

df.drop('index',inplace=True,axis=1)
df.drop('',inplace=True,axis=1)

X =df

X = df[['', '', '', '', '1', '2', '3', '4', '', '',
       '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '']]

tsne = TSNE(n_components=2, random_state = 0, perplexity = 30, n_iter = 1000)
X_embedded = tsne.fit_transform(X)

ddf = pd.concat([df, pd.DataFrame(X_embedded, columns = ['col1', 'col2'])], axis = 1)
ddf[''] = index_df['']
article_list = ddf[''].unique()
ddf[''] = index_df['index']

colors =  ["lightgreen", "red", "pink", "g", "orange", "cyan", "k", "b"]
plt.figure(figsize = (30, 30))
for i , v in enumerate(article_list):
    tmp_df = ddf[ddf[''] == v]
    plt.scatter(tmp_df['col1'],  
                tmp_df['col2'],
                label = v,
                color = colors[i],
               s = 1500)

for x, y, name in zip(ddf['col1'], ddf['col2'],ddf['']):
    plt.text(x+0.5, y, name,fontsize=18)

plt.legend(fontsize = 30)
plt.savefig('TSNE.png')
